	dprr:hasNoteText "In MRR 2.27, and Index, 583, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.315, no. 305, 109 or 108 B.C. The whole entry should be transferred to MRR 1.549, and Lutatius listed as quaestor in 109 or 108 B.C.\n" ;
